27757830eca8d31c6a7","tid":1604282,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f716b366799384378fa0079f3f53ac3c0df1329b","tid":1604282,"uid":54511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"係 連登都好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有留意 就知 咩咩香港人權法無用 咩咩外國唔會理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實睇正負評 就知 連登內鬼都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:53:42.000Z","msg":"咪係，乜都唔理就鬧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>【突發】史上首次！超過55位 英國議員 直斥中共違反《聯合聲明》，攬炒團隊成功發動跨黨聯署！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n19/9政府公然藐視《中英聯合聲明》，挑釁香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3v7KSvz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3v7KSvz.png&h=9c57359c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多番攻防戰之後，我同團隊嘗試喺國際戰線上再下一城，<strong>謹此 宣布，2/10攬炒團隊成功發動：</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong> 「英國國會跨黨派聯署」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>史上首次出現58位議員不分黨派，直斥中共嚴重違反《中英聯合聲明》！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLbS1Nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLbS1Nv.jpg&h=76ab4761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4cVsQFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4cVsQFY.jpg&h=514c7def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1aUxFCf8SnKsv7RFGiQvCLvgyl_m5BQWf?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1aUxFCf8SnKsv7RFGiQvCLvgyl_m5BQWf%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1cTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=e63acc37\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1aUxFCf8SnKsv7RFGiQvCLvgyl_m5BQWf?usp=sharing</a></span><br />\n<br />\n值得一提嘅係，名單入面有<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">前英國外相、現任影子內閣、外交事務委員會 等重量級人物</span></span></strong>背書支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的確，英國近年被Brexit 困擾，支援未夠，但係基於歷史淵源，同國際條約依個籌碼，幾困難我地都會打依條戰線。<br />\n<br />\n幸運地，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">經過香港人過去四個月努力</span></strong>，再加上7月大家託付俾我地嘅資金支持，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">英國戰線漸見曙光</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，攬炒團隊深信國際本土雙戰線上，無論中共下一步棋係點，香港人都有能力反制。<br />\n<br />\n唔理佢推咩緊急法、蒙面法，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>歷史上暴政必亡，再撐落去，我地就會贏。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVVo74W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVVo74W.gif&h=6741fe6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n寧化飛灰，不作浮塵<br />\nIF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US.</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">正牌攬炒Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/StirFryChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStirFryChannel&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1cTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=464212b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StirFryChannel</a>"},{"pid":"25e83ca2507e906b8d12607960bff2938ebe4b4f","tid":1604282,"uid":31520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"因為國際勢力先係政府中共最驚既野<br />\n緊係全力分裂你地唔比你地connect喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊話外國啲措施冇撚用幫唔到手<br />\n一邊搵機會抺黑示威者 羞化形象"}]}